<p begin='00:02:29.683' end='00:02:31.752' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>ELEPHANT POACHING AND TERRORISM.<br/>LIKE WHEN YOU LOOK AT WESTGATE</span></p>
