<p begin='00:05:03.203' end='00:05:05.172' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; SO, WHAT CAN BE DONE NOW WHEN<br/>YOU SAY WELL THIS IS SOMETHING</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:05.205' end='00:05:07.875' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THAT WE CAN DO. I MEAN, WE TRIED<br/>THAT WITH MILEAGE FOR OUR</span></p>
